reg_info.reg_name_text: Delegation by Public Service Commission under Subsection 44 (4) of the Act
reg_info.citation: O. Reg. 148/10: DELEGATION BY PUBLIC SERVICE COMMISSION UNDER SUBSECTION 44 (4) OF THE ACT

content.section: Delegation, public servants appointed to work in Commission public body
content.content: 1. For a Commission public body listed in Column 1 of Table 1, the individual who holds the position listed in Column 2 of the Table is prescribed for the purposes of clause 44 (4) (a) of the Act.  O. Reg. 148/10, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. For a Commission public body listed in Column 1 of Table 1, the individual who holds the position listed in Column 2 of the Table is prescribed for the purposes of clause 44 (4) (a) of the Act.  O. Reg. 148/10, s. 1.

content.content: 2. Omitted (revokes other Regulations).  O. Reg. 148/10, s. 2.
